                <listEvent>
                    <event>
                        <desc>
                            Because<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2468">Paul</persName>has an ordinarily simple disposition, <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2417">Solon</persName>should not frighten him like a child by forcing him to sign documents.
